#STOP
10000
-1.0

#RUN ===============================================

#SCHEME
2                       nOrder (1 or 2)
Linde                 FluxType  1=Roe, 2=Rusanov, 3=Linde
mc                  LimiterType ! Only for nordder=2
1.2

#STOP
25000
-1.0

#RUN ===================================================

#SCHEME
2                       nOrder (1 or 2)
Linde                 FluxType  1=Roe, 2=Rusanov, 3=Linde
